                    <span>It is no doubt MLK's speeches are great and did alot<br>to shape American thinking.  Unfortunately, I can only <br>play the first 2 CDs on my CD player.  I have a friend<br>who has a CD player that can play all of them.  Apparently<br>it has something to do with the index numbering on each<br>CD.  Instead of each CD starting at 1 it starts where the previous CD left off.  I wouldn't take a chance that this<br>product won't play in your CD player.  I think it is very<br>unfortunate that I paid so much for the complete set of speeches<br>and I can't listen to most of it.<br>I WOULD WAIT UNTIL THE NEXT VERSION COMES OUT THAT CORRECTS THIS<br>FLAW.<br>It would have been also nice to have some text to accompany the <br>audio CDs.</span>
                  
